00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:21,520
不是我说啊，你俩看起来好像没那么开心嘛
If you don’t mind me saying, neither of you look very happy...

619
00:40:23,120 --> 00:40:24,200
好嘞
There you go.

620
00:40:24,640 --> 00:40:28,080
从他五岁开始我就知道了，这孩子有足球上的天赋
I knew this since when he was five, he had the skills of football.

621
00:40:28,160 --> 00:40:29,320
他带球的时候
He was like...

622
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:32,640
就跟台机器一样
a machine when he's running with the ball.

623
00:40:32,680 --> 00:40:35,680
很多大俱乐部当时都在追求他
All the big clubs were chasing him.

624
00:40:35,800 --> 00:40:37,200
我们到了阿森纳
We came to Arsenal.

625
00:40:37,320 --> 00:40:40,200
他们说，“我们希望他能成为一名阿森纳球员”
They said, "We want him to be an Arsenal player."

626
00:40:40,840 --> 00:40:43,080
好在我们找到了一个热刺的人
Luckily we found a person from Tottenham.

627
00:40:43,160 --> 00:40:45,600
“明天把他带来托特纳姆球场，我们要定他了”
"Bring him tomorrow,
at Tottenham, we like him."

628
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:47,640
周六，我们就对阵阿森纳来了一场
Saturday, we had a game against Arsenal,

629
00:40:47,760 --> 00:40:49,440
他进球了，我记得是两球来着
so he scored, I think, two goals.

630
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:54,520
比赛结束当场他们就拿合同来找他签了
Straight away after the match, they gave us the contract and he signed.

631
00:40:54,600 --> 00:40:57,040
咱这里也跟贾菲特来两张？
Shall we do a couple of pictures with Japhet here?

632
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:57,920
好
Yeah.

633
00:40:58,000 --> 00:41:01,520
我觉得他应该知道，我对他和对整个家庭有多感激
I think he knows how grateful I am of not only him but my whole family.

634
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:05,360
每个人都在为我付出，努力，才能成就我的今天
Everyone has chipped in and played a part for me to be in this moment today.

635
00:41:05,440 --> 00:41:06,800
这仅仅是一个开始
This is just the beginning.

636
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:09,640
从现在开始，我要继续努力付出
This is the just the start and from here just to kick on,

637
00:41:09,760 --> 00:41:12,520
保持对进步的渴望，继续我被派上场对战利物浦
just making sure I stay hungry and keep doing the things

638
00:41:12,600 --> 00:41:14,520
那时候背后的努力
that got me to play against Liverpool.

639
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:17,640
按照教练的要求去做，保持进步
Keep doing what the manager asks, keep improving and make sure

640
00:41:17,680 --> 00:41:20,320
我还不能骄傲自满，毕竟我还没有功成名就
I don’t get complacent and I don’t think I’ve made it

641
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:21,960
还需要继续的去努力
and I don’t need to try anymore

642
00:41:22,040 --> 00:41:23,520
这才是对我而言最重要的
so that’s the big one for me.

643
00:41:23,680 --> 00:41:27,080
我们对贾菲特和他本赛季的进步感到非常的欣喜
We're excited about Japhet and the way he's progressed this season.

644
00:41:27,160 --> 00:41:30,640
我们有一群非常优秀的年轻球员
We’ve got a good group of good young players,

645
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:34,920
没准夏天我们还能再添置两到三个球员，甚至更多
hopefully, we will add two or three players this summer, maybe more.

646
00:41:35,680 --> 00:41:38,560
但对于球迷而言是很难理解的，球迷总是说
It’s difficult for fans because fans always say,

647
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:42,040
“我们得签下这个球员，我们得签下那个球员”
"We should be signing this player, we should be signing that player."

648
00:41:42,120 --> 00:41:44,480
我们的转会预算非常充足
We've been backed in terms of transfer funds,

649
00:41:44,560 --> 00:41:47,280
我们也知道球队的弱点在哪，与强队的差距在哪，若泽也很清楚
we know the holes, the gaps. I think José is very clear

650
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:50,560
球队里大概有三到四个位置是他重点想要补强的
that there is three to four positions he wants to improve on.

651
00:41:51,480 --> 00:41:55,920
我们总是跟青训营保持无间合作
We work together always in cohesion with the academy,

652
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:59,040
若泽，丹尼尔，我们都有一个长远的计划
with José, with Daniel, with a long-term plan.

653
00:41:59,120 --> 00:42:01,080
冲啊塞斯！干得不错！
Go on Sess! Yes, Sess!

654
00:42:01,160 --> 00:42:04,160
我认为这就是我们跟其他俱乐部不一样的地方
And I think that is the difference between us and other clubs

655
00:42:04,200 --> 00:42:07,880
我们更加着眼于未来，而不是仅仅聚焦于当下
that we've got to always look further down the line rather than today.

