00:42:43,760 --> 00:42:44,760
官媒
Official media.

668
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:45,960
官媒？
Official?

669
00:42:46,360 --> 00:42:48,880
取消掉了，没有禁赛令了
They’ve lifted it, there is no ban.

670
00:42:50,640 --> 00:42:51,960
- 卧槽没了？  - 确实没了
- No ban?  - No ban.

671
00:42:52,040 --> 00:42:53,200
- 曼城是吧？  - 嗯
- Man City? - Yeah.

672
00:42:55,440 --> 00:42:58,320
取消曼城禁赛令的决定
The decision to overturn Manchester City’s ban

673
00:42:58,400 --> 00:43:01,320
意味着如果要想争夺下赛季的欧联席位
means that to guarantee Europa League football next season,

