676
00:43:09,160 --> 00:43:10,800
咱得都赢下来了
We have to win everything.

677
00:43:11,320 --> 00:43:12,840
三场比赛全部梭哈
We need to win three games.

678
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:23,280
热刺今年只在客场赢过一场比赛
Spurs have only won away from home once this year.

679
00:43:24,480 --> 00:43:26,560
下一轮是客战纽卡斯尔
Next up is a trip to Newcastle.

680
00:43:29,520 --> 00:43:32,680
咱三场全赢，欧联到手
We win the three matches, we get Europa League.

681
00:43:32,800 --> 00:43:34,960
赢球了，咱就有的踢
If we win our matches, we are there.

682
00:43:35,040 --> 00:43:37,920
所以不多哔哔了，必须拿下
We have to win, so no more talk.

683
