685
00:43:49,720 --> 00:43:51,360
贝尔温起脚传中
Bergwijn's delivery...

686
00:43:51,440 --> 00:43:53,880
凯恩头球精彩命中！
Harry Kane with an excellent header.

687
00:43:55,440 --> 00:43:57,240
热刺全取三分
Tottenham take all three points,

688
00:43:58,040 --> 00:43:59,880
哈里·凯恩梅开二度
with Harry Kane scoring two

