00:43:59,960 --> 00:44:02,760
将自己的职业生涯总进球数提升到了200球以上
to take his tally to over two hundred career goals.

690
00:44:02,840 --> 00:44:06,480
200球是一种神奇的体验
Two hundred goals is just an amazing feeling.

691
00:44:06,560 --> 00:44:09,560
职业生涯中会经历大大小小的里程碑时刻
During your career you kind of go through landmarks like that

692
00:44:09,640 --> 00:44:12,840
当时可能都没有什么感觉，但等到我退役
and you don’t fully take it in. It will be when I finish playing,

693
00:44:12,920 --> 00:44:15,840
会看我的职业生涯，才会发现原来已经达到了这么多成就
you look back and you realise what you have actually done.

694
00:44:16,280 --> 00:44:18,120
对于我而言，我达到了200球里程碑
For me, I’ve scored two hundred goals

695
00:44:18,200 --> 00:44:21,920
但更重要的是，什么时候我能打进我的下100个进球，甚至下200个进球
but it’s about how quickly can I get the next hundred, or next two hundred.

