00:44:39,680 --> 00:44:44,560
我觉得当你的个人生活非常顺利的时候
I think there’s a big part of it when your personal life is going well,

701
00:44:44,640 --> 00:44:47,400
很大程度上也能推动你的职业生涯顺利走下去
it definitely relates to your professional life as well.

702
00:44:47,480 --> 00:44:48,600
爸比？
Daddy?

