710
00:45:08,600 --> 00:45:10,880
你们觉得爸爸会命中嘛？嗯？
Do you think Daddy's gonna score a goal? Yeah?

711
00:45:12,400 --> 00:45:15,320
爸爸加油！爸比加油！
Go Daddy! Daddy, go!

