00:45:58,200 --> 00:46:01,960
场下的生活非常的精彩，场上也一样
Things are exciting off the pitch and they’re exciting on the pitch as well.

724
00:46:02,040 --> 00:46:05,480
我们赛季末的表现非常出色，所以希望我们能争取到欧联席位吧
We're finishing strong so hopefully we can get a Europa League spot

725
00:46:05,560 --> 00:46:09,400
下赛季至少还能四线作战
and at least be in four competitions next year.

