732
00:46:33,240 --> 00:46:34,280
我们能赢的
Yeah, we'll win.

733
00:46:34,360 --> 00:46:36,160
一锤定音了，加油！
Massive game, come on!

734
00:46:37,000 --> 00:46:40,960
凯恩牢牢地拿住了球，漂亮的传给小孙
Here is Kane to hold it up and he’s done really well to set away Son.

735
00:46:41,560 --> 00:46:42,600
孙兴慜
Heung-min Son...

