00:47:05,640 --> 00:47:08,680
八天打赢了三场比赛
and have won three in the space of eight days.

741
00:47:09,320 --> 00:47:13,040
恭喜你们再下一城，非常全面的表现
Congratulations on the win. I mean, that seemed quite comprehensive really.

742
00:47:13,120 --> 00:47:15,240
你怎么评价球队今天的表现
What did you make of the performance today?

743
00:47:15,320 --> 00:47:19,160
我对球队非常欣慰，因为这场比赛的压力非常大
I am very happy because it’s a game with a lot of pressure to us,

744
00:47:19,240 --> 00:47:22,760
我们拼到了最后一刻
and we are fighting until we can.

