755
00:47:57,080 --> 00:47:59,520
他们将被带上屋顶
They're about to be taken up on to the roof,

756
00:47:59,600 --> 00:48:01,600
距离球场地面150英尺
a hundred and fifty feet above the pitch

757
00:48:02,680 --> 00:48:06,160
他们将成为球场“勇闯天涯”项目的首批体验者
and be amongst the first to try out The Dare Skywalk.

758
00:48:15,600 --> 00:48:19,000
你说我要不要先给球队交代一下周天怎么搞，以往万一我就交代在这了
Do you want me to tell the team for Sunday in case I don’t come back?

759
00:48:24,400 --> 00:48:26,520
我感觉VAR比这个还恐怖
I think VAR is more scary than this.

760
00:48:26,600 --> 00:48:31,880
你明明进球了还得在那等，算是不算
When you score a goal and you are there waiting, goal, no goal.

761
00:48:34,400 --> 00:48:38,240
以我们热刺的体量来讲，咱们的球员跟球迷
Tottenham is a size of a club that our players and our fans

762
00:48:38,560 --> 00:48:41,520
都希望我们，也都习惯了我们每年有欧战踢
expect us, and have got used to us being in Europe,

763
00:48:41,600 --> 00:48:44,760
但是你也知道，咱这个赛季过的那是一个难上加难
but you know, we have had a very, very difficult season.

764
00:48:44,840 --> 00:48:48,880
所以我觉得以这种成绩收官，虽然不是那么的令人满意
So I think to end up in a place, not that it’s satisfactory,

765
00:48:48,960 --> 00:48:51,880
但至少，咱还有欧战能踢
um, but to end up still being in Europe,

766
00:48:51,960 --> 00:48:56,800
在这种情况之下，我觉得吧，也是一个能接受的成绩
I think, in the circumstances, will be a good place to end up.

767
00:49:04,400 --> 00:49:05,560
噢！
Oh!

768
00:49:11,080 --> 00:49:13,000
幸好我有个东西可以抓着
I'm glad I got something to hold onto.

769
00:49:14,280 --> 00:49:18,560
这地方最合适把经纪人带来谈判了
It’s the best place to bring the agents to negotiate.

770
00:49:20,400 --> 00:49:23,880
哟，那是爷的教练席，额滴个乖乖
Oh, look at my bench. Oh, my god.

771
00:49:27,080 --> 00:49:28,360
牛逼普拉斯
Incredible.

772
00:49:29,040 --> 00:49:33,800
我向来每年都是有欧战踢的，所以我也不希望这是我头一遭
I always qualified for Europe so I don’t want to be the first time

773
00:49:33,880 --> 00:49:35,720
欧战没得踢
of not qualifying for Europe.

774
00:49:35,800 --> 00:49:38,640
于我，于球员，于球迷来说，都是非常重要的
It’s very important for me, for the players, for the fans,

775
00:49:38,720 --> 00:49:40,120
对俱乐部的每一个人来说都是
for the club, for everybody.

776
00:49:40,200 --> 00:49:45,560
对于球员的精神层面，保持这种骄傲也是非常非常重要的
But for the mental, by the pride side, it’s very, very important.

777
00:49:49,720 --> 00:49:53,040
来到赛季的收官战，热刺在积分榜排名第八
Going into the last match, Tottenham sit in eighth.

778
00:49:53,120 --> 00:49:57,440
狼队目前暂时以一分领先，热刺只要能比狼队踢得好
If they can secure a better result than Wolves, who are just one point ahead,

779
00:49:57,520 --> 00:50:01,280
他们就能顺利确保进军下赛季的欧联杯
they will guarantee themselves a place in next season's Europa League.

780
00:50:02,960 --> 00:50:04,840
你们都吭哧瘪肚12个月了
You are working for twelve months.

781
00:50:04,920 --> 00:50:06,280
从他妈的去年6月份开始
Fucking since July.

782
00:50:07,000 --> 00:50:09,440
加油，就没理由咱不给自己个交代
Come on, it's impossible we don't do it.

783
00:50:09,560 --> 00:50:11,840
来吧来吧，嘿！冲啊！给爷冲！
Come on, hey! Let’s go, hey! Let’s go!

784
00:50:11,920 --> 00:50:13,200
兄弟们！干他们，冲就完了！
Let's go. Let's go, boys!

785
00:50:14,360 --> 00:50:18,200
对热刺来说，本赛季格外的非比寻常、跌宕起伏
For Spurs, it has been the most unusual and dramatic of campaigns.

786
00:50:19,560 --> 00:50:24,040
一路从停摆、波切蒂诺下课、穆里尼奥接任
Along with the lockdown, Pochettino’s departure and Mourinho’s arrival,

787
00:50:24,120 --> 00:50:29,080
埃里克森转会，阿尔德维雷尔得续约，凯恩、孙兴慜、洛里、西索科接连受伤
Eriksen leaving, Alderweireld staying, injuries to Kane, Son, Lloris and Sissoko.

788
00:50:29,320 --> 00:50:32,480
太多太多故事了，但是在穆里尼奥麾下的第一个完整赛季
Too many stories to mention, but claiming Europa League football

789
00:50:32,560 --> 00:50:35,120
成功进军下赛季的欧联杯
ahead of a first full season under Mourinho

790
00:50:35,200 --> 00:50:38,760
也算是一个不错的方式来结束2019/20赛季
would be a good way to end 2019/20.

791
00:50:41,760 --> 00:50:45,440
西索科…凯恩…
Sissoko... Kane...

792
00:50:45,520 --> 00:50:49,160
精准找到卢卡斯，孙兴慜在中路跑位绝佳
well-weighted into Lucas Moura. Now Son’s made a good run into the middle.

793
00:50:49,240 --> 00:50:50,240
洛塞尔索
Here’s Lo Celso...

794
00:50:50,320 --> 00:50:52,120
一脚劲射
who will have a crack at goal.

795
00:50:53,600 --> 00:50:58,160
目前切尔西0-0狼队，所以狼队暂位列积分榜第六
Chelsea nil, Wolves nil currently so Wolves is hanging onto sixth.

796
00:50:58,240 --> 00:51:00,680
他们只要比热刺的结果强就行
They only have to match Spurs result.

797
00:51:02,800 --> 00:51:05,360
洛塞尔索，直塞凯恩
Lo Celso slips in Kane...

798
00:51:08,640 --> 00:51:11,600
打门！手起刀落！
who pulls the trigger in emphatic fashion.

799
00:51:13,160 --> 00:51:15,280
典型的哈里·凯恩式进球
Typical Harry Kane.

800
00:51:19,080 --> 00:51:22,200
那么热刺暂时来到了积分榜第六
So, at the moment Spurs are moving up to sixth.

801
00:51:23,240 --> 00:51:24,480
卢卡斯·莫拉
Lucas Moura...

802
00:51:24,560 --> 00:51:28,160
找到了空挡，他能拿到球吗，他拿到了！
looks to spring into a gap, will he meet the ball? Yes, he does.

803
00:51:28,240 --> 00:51:29,440
漂亮！
That was brilliant work.

804
00:51:31,920 --> 00:51:33,040
来到中场休息
It is half time,

805
00:51:34,320 --> 00:51:37,000
顺便一提，来自斯坦福桥的突发新闻
and by the way, breaking news from Stamford Bridge,

806
00:51:37,080 --> 00:51:39,600
切尔西对狼队拔得头筹
Chelsea have taken the lead against Wolves.

807
00:51:39,680 --> 00:51:41,320
无疑是利好热刺的消息
That’s great news for Spurs.

808
00:51:41,400 --> 00:51:45,040
如果局面持续到比赛结束，热刺将挺进欧联
If it all stays like this, Spurs are going into the Europa League.

809
00:51:45,880 --> 00:51:49,760
咱防的不错，但是还得控制住比赛局面
We are defending quite well but we need to control the game.

810
00:51:50,320 --> 00:51:52,920
咱得更为稳定一点
We need to be more, more consistent.

811
00:51:53,000 --> 00:51:56,080
如果联赛现在就收官
If the league finished now,

812
00:51:56,160 --> 00:51:58,200
咱能捞到一个第六
in this moment, we are sixth,

813
00:51:58,280 --> 00:52:03,000
但是咱得赢下比赛，随时可能有新的变局
but we need to win the game. The game can go in two directions.

814
00:52:03,080 --> 00:52:04,880
加油兄弟们！加油！
Come on, lads. Come on!

815
00:52:11,400 --> 00:52:14,000
看样子只要一场平局热刺就能安稳收官
As things stand even a draw would be enough for Spurs

816
00:52:14,080 --> 00:52:16,480
因为狼队目前0-2落后
because Wolves are trailing two-nil.

817
00:52:17,120 --> 00:52:21,000
穆里尼奥已经知道之一消息了，但他不想让他的球员分心
And Mourinho will know the score line, but he will want his players to focus.

818
00:52:21,080 --> 00:52:22,240
我们的球！
Our ball!

819
00:52:22,320 --> 00:52:25,400
奥里耶在角旗区遭到紧逼
Serge Aurier under real pressure near the corner flag.

820
00:52:29,160 --> 00:52:31,040
解围！再来！
Away! Again!

821
00:52:34,080 --> 00:52:36,280
热刺惨遭当头棒喝
And it’s a big blow for Spurs.

822
00:52:39,280 --> 00:52:41,120
热刺目前输不起
Spurs cannot afford to lose here,

823
00:52:42,280 --> 00:52:44,600
因为但凡他们输一个，他们都保不住第六了
because if they lose, they will not claim sixth

824
00:52:44,680 --> 00:52:47,200
斯坦福桥那边干啥都不顶用
no matter what happens at Stamford Bridge.

825
00:52:49,680 --> 00:52:50,760
乔尔·沃德
Joel Ward...

826
00:52:50,840 --> 00:52:53,200
噢！再次命中横梁
Oh, it's hit against the frame of the goal.

827
00:52:53,280 --> 00:52:54,400
看球啊！
Look, look the ball!

828
00:52:54,480 --> 00:52:57,080
这个位置危险了，阿尤
Precarious position this, Ayew!

829
00:52:58,240 --> 00:52:59,920
现在进入伤停补时阶段
So we are now into added time.

830
00:53:02,840 --> 00:53:04,360
水晶宫的球
It will be a Palace ball.

831
00:53:08,280 --> 00:53:10,320
危险的传球
Delivery is dangerous...

832
00:53:10,880 --> 00:53:12,360
稍稍偏出
and it's just wide.

833
00:53:15,440 --> 00:53:20,640
全场比赛结束哨响，狼队保持落后，已经足够了
That is the full-time whistle and with Wolves losing, this will be enough.

834
00:53:20,720 --> 00:53:23,880
穆里尼奥和他的主教团队正在庆祝
Mourinho and his coaching staff are celebrating.

835
00:53:25,360 --> 00:53:30,200
我作为教练已经有点被惯坏了，因为我的职业生涯早就习惯了
I’m quite a spoilt coach because my career was always about

836
00:53:30,280 --> 00:53:32,880
赢冠军，赢冠军，赢冠军
winning trophies, winning trophies, winning trophies.

837
00:53:33,000 --> 00:53:37,800
我还从来没想象过自己会为了赛季末排名第六而兴高采烈
I would never imagine myself celebrating in the end of the season finishing sixth,

838
00:53:39,880 --> 00:53:43,760
但是我把他们从十四名带到了第六名
but to arrive fourteenth and to finish sixth,

839
00:53:44,440 --> 00:53:45,520
也还算不错是吧？
a good achievement?

840
00:53:47,840 --> 00:53:48,840
至少我自己是这么认为的
I would say so.

841
00:54:03,880 --> 00:54:07,040
[♪ AJ Tracey & Mabel: “West Ten”]

842
00:54:22,640 --> 00:54:26,000
我接手热刺的时候，热刺是一家比现在小得多的俱乐部
Tottenham when I took over was a much smaller club than it is today,

843
00:54:26,080 --> 00:54:30,120
我看着这家俱乐部就像一头沉睡中的猛兽
I saw this club as a club that was really a sleeping giant.

844
00:54:30,960 --> 00:54:33,120
咱现在到了这个阶段得赢点什么了
We are now in a period where we need to win.

845
00:54:33,200 --> 00:54:37,520
讲道理，我一直是个热刺球迷，我希望俱乐部越来越好
You know, I’m a spurs fan and I want to see this club continue to grow

846
00:54:38,240 --> 00:54:39,880
我也想要看到冠军头衔
and I want to see trophies.

847
00:54:41,040 --> 00:54:43,840
各位，我稍微说两句哈
Can I just have your attention for a minute, please?

848
00:54:47,120 --> 00:54:53,000
首先，我想要感谢大家在这个艰难的赛季的所有付出
Firstly, I want to, uh, thank you all for what has been a difficult season

849
00:54:53,080 --> 00:54:54,480
无论是场上还是场下
both on and off the pitch,

850
00:54:54,560 --> 00:54:57,560
无论世界上今天发生了啥
and what’s going on in the world today.

851
00:54:57,640 --> 00:55:00,800
咱以一个不错的成绩收官，我个人还是很满意的
I’m very pleased that we're finishing the season in a good place

852
00:55:00,880 --> 00:55:03,600
但咱们队里有两个队员
but two members of our team,

853
00:55:03,680 --> 00:55:06,880
很遗憾下赛季不会再跟我们并肩作战了
as we know, won’t be back next year, unfortunately.

854
00:55:06,960 --> 00:55:10,520
来吧，米歇尔、杨，你俩上来吧
So Michel and Jan, I would like you to come up here.

855
00:55:16,320 --> 00:55:19,120
你们两个人都毫无疑问是球队的铁血功勋
Both you guys have been an absolute credit to this club,

856
00:55:19,760 --> 00:55:23,000
我们非常感谢你们的付出，这里随时欢迎你们回来
we would like to thank you very much, you are always welcome back.

857
00:55:23,080 --> 00:55:26,360
无论你们将来的决定是什么，我们都衷心祝愿你们一路都好
Wish you both the best of luck in whatever you decide to do,

858
00:55:26,440 --> 00:55:29,560
我们给你们买了个小礼物
and we have a small gift that we bought both of you.

859
00:55:30,640 --> 00:55:33,560
一人一块手表，背后还会给你们刻字
We bought you both a watch and we'll get something engraved

860
00:55:33,640 --> 00:55:34,640
专属定制
on the back for you.

861
00:55:37,000 --> 00:55:38,080
非常感谢大家
Thank you very much.

862
00:55:39,280 --> 00:55:42,480
这赛季着实是不容易
I think this season is a difficult one,

863
00:55:42,560 --> 00:55:46,640
但未来会越来越好的，我会永远想念大家
the future will be bright and I’m going to miss everyone.

864
00:55:46,720 --> 00:55:48,320
感谢你们所作的一切
So, thank you for everything.

865
00:55:52,400 --> 00:55:55,280
非常感谢大家，八年前我刚来的时候
Thank you very much, I came here eight years ago

866
00:55:55,360 --> 00:55:57,720
跟现在大不一样
in a total different environment.

867
00:55:57,840 --> 00:56:02,360
这些年很多东西都变了，无论是作为俱乐部还是作为球队
A lot has changed over the years, where we are now as a club, as a team,

868
00:56:02,440 --> 00:56:04,720
我为大家而骄傲
you have made me very proud.

869
00:56:04,920 --> 00:56:06,960
大家对我来说意义非凡
You guys mean so much to me,

870
00:56:07,040 --> 00:56:10,360
我很确定未来我没办法再找到这样的一直球队了
I know for sure I will never find a team like this again.

871
00:56:17,080 --> 00:56:21,080
我一般不怎么看球，完整看完一场90分钟的球赛
I don’t watch a lot of football. I think in total 90 minutes I watch,

872
00:56:21,160 --> 00:56:23,240
我印象中一个赛季不超过五次
not even five games a season,

873
00:56:24,760 --> 00:56:29,360
但是下个赛季我会尽可能的收看每一场热刺的比赛
but I will watch every Spurs game that I can next season.

874
00:56:29,440 --> 00:56:32,560
大都知道，球迷们管你叫超人詹
As we know, the fans call you Super Jan,

875
00:56:32,640 --> 00:56:35,920
所以大伙儿也给你准备了一个礼物
so we’ve also got a gift that’s actually from all your teammates.

876
00:56:40,200 --> 00:56:44,240
他们比赛之后我会给每个人打Facetime的，我一定会
I know, everyone I will FaceTime them after the game, I definitely know I will.

877
00:56:44,320 --> 00:56:47,440
他们下赛季很有机会赢下大把的冠军奖杯
And they have got good chances of winning something next season

878
00:56:47,520 --> 00:56:49,280
所以也祝他们一切都好
so hopefully for them they can now.

879
00:56:49,360 --> 00:56:52,600
我会一直关注他们的，这会是一种很特别的感觉
And yeah, I will follow them and it will be very special.

880
00:56:55,960 --> 00:57:02,120
热刺在过去的12个月里踢了52场比赛，史无前例最长的赛季
Spurs have played 52 games over 12 months, the longest season in their history.

881
00:57:04,000 --> 00:57:06,920
一个跌宕起伏的赛季，跟做过山车一样
An up and down season, been of a rollercoaster of a season,

882
00:57:07,000 --> 00:57:11,480
从我个人的角度来说，伤病这些东西都是这种感觉
obviously from a personal point of view of being injured and things like that.

883
00:57:11,560 --> 00:57:13,720
但是从球队的角度来说
And just from a team point of view, whenever

884
00:57:13,800 --> 00:57:16,320
赛季初是一个教练，赛季结束换成了另一个
you start with one manager and finish with another,

885
00:57:16,400 --> 00:57:18,520
那这注定是一个不平凡的赛季
it means it’s going to be a strange season.

886
00:57:19,600 --> 00:57:23,120
我们这赛季经历了不少困难的低谷，这没什么掩饰的
There's no hiding the fact that we went through a few difficult spells,

887
00:57:23,200 --> 00:57:26,880
但是你环顾四周，看看咱球队这个实力
and when we look at the quality we have in the team and around the place,

888
00:57:26,960 --> 00:57:30,680
所有东西，从训练场到球场，每一样东西，我觉得
everything we have from training ground to stadium, everything is, I think,

889
00:57:30,760 --> 00:57:32,880
咱就是欧冠级别的
you know, the quality is Champions League.

890
00:57:34,240 --> 00:57:37,840
没拿到前四诚然令人难过
To not get the top four, it was painful

891
00:57:37,920 --> 00:57:40,960
毕竟欧冠是每个球员每个赛季都想踢的比赛
because Champions League everyone wants to play every season,

892
00:57:41,040 --> 00:57:44,080
但至少我们还有欧联杯可以踢
but at least the minimum you get is Europa League

893
00:57:44,200 --> 00:57:48,320
但愿我们能赢下点冠军奖杯，毕竟实力在这
and hopefully we will win some trophies because the quality is there

894
00:57:48,400 --> 00:57:51,560
跟着教练走下去肯定能行的，我丝毫不怀疑
but I’m sure with this manager, we will do it.

895
00:57:54,240 --> 00:57:56,880
我非常期待下赛季的开踢，因为
I look forward to the beginning of next season because

896
00:57:57,560 --> 00:58:01,840
这几个月来我们的相处，我们的付出
everything we did, all these months that we spent together,

897
00:58:01,920 --> 00:58:05,160
我觉得在未来都会收获回报的
I think are very, very important for the future.

898
00:58:06,400 --> 00:58:10,320
我们已经准备好作为一个强大的集体面对任何困难了
We are ready to go through everything like a strong family

899
00:58:11,480 --> 00:58:15,280
这是一个坚实的基础
and that creates us a good base,

900
00:58:15,960 --> 00:58:18,080
但我想做到更好
